{"tid":334265,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣駕照設計超簡陋？　比較完外國網友怒了","createTime":"2017-07-24T14:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T08:22:26.000Z","uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb7b5422369a8004f9760d444dfc30be3525f465","tid":334265,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:16:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170724/640_2e22508d8e43d3791705c89e82c05ea7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170724%2F640_2e22508d8e43d3791705c89e82c05ea7.jpg&h=1205859d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中華民國的駕照好簡陋！您也這麼覺得嗎？翻攝自PTT<br />\n<br />\n有網友在PTT八卦板發文詢問「為何中華民國政府的駕照如此簡陋？」，他指出「駕照象徵一個人對交通工具的行駛許可，從皮夾掏出來的機率甚至略高於身分證，但本島政府做出來的駕照竟然只是一張紙？」，他也舉例美國、韓國以及日本駕照，都是好看又耐用的硬卡式駕照，反觀台灣的駕照是紙做的、包膜也只包正面，卡面設計更是慘不忍睹，大概只有中國的駕照跟台灣差不多，但他們至少是「雙面護貝」，也都還比台灣的駕照耐用。<br />\n<br />\n文章引發網友討論，有網友認同說「台灣駕照紙糊的，硬式卡比較好」「跟舊式身分證一樣時期的產物，不過廢物交通部不想改版」「現在的駕照好歹放得進皮夾，行照尺寸更大放不下，根本活化石」「而且日本駕照是內含RFID晶片的，警察碰一下就能讀資料」，但也有網友解釋「目前政府有在研議身分證、健保卡、駕照合在同一張塑膠卡，所以紙本駕照暫時才沒有改掉。」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170724/420_1e546f34dbec436bda1f39ae96bae85f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170724%2F420_1e546f34dbec436bda1f39ae96bae85f.jpg&h=27f46323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170724/420_e8b2684a2c7703cf84b000b0d8535246.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170724%2F420_e8b2684a2c7703cf84b000b0d8535246.jpg&h=5ccd3e8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170724/420_f68385de9ea5dafb4e5d030a943c6bea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170724%2F420_f68385de9ea5dafb4e5d030a943c6bea.jpg&h=9cb2fc4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國、韓國以及日本駕照都是硬卡式，好看耐用且多功能。翻攝自PTT<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170724/420_5d6e3d540319b03c65312f4a79ffff96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170724%2F420_5d6e3d540319b03c65312f4a79ffff96.jpg&h=8964eadc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國的駕照跟台灣一樣都是紙做的，但他們是兩面護貝。翻攝自PTT<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170724/1167414/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Flife%2F20170724%2F1167414%2F&d=786xU7PnK6mKZu4gmYOL3RxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=fb21d0d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20170724/1167414/</a>"},{"pid":"5311c385ee9801fd2db036b780a7827a9696364b","tid":334265,"uid":75154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07df8925b753cea5e0c31518398cc09ce7c09673","tid":334265,"uid":5278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:56:20.000Z","msg":"香港相都冇"},{"pid":"4e48ac5781186111c7d824526931797faa7210d1","tid":334265,"uid":96453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:56:27.000Z","msg":"張相貼上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1e839afd9c6b8eaded43b32630bebb49ee69f9","tid":334265,"uid":9230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:18:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港相都冇</blockquote><br />\n所以熄匙之後係車牌+身分證"},{"pid":"a2226bd364684ff904017c3ebe6cb0983e96d8bb","tid":334265,"uid":15921,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:12:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港相都冇</blockquote><br />\n所以熄匙之後係車牌+身分證</blockquote><br />\n好羨慕人地車牌當